graph LR
    CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator<br/>v1.9.0]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    CodeFlare -->|extends with<br/>OAuth, mTLS,<br/>NetworkPolicy| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.1.0<br/>REQUIRED]
    CodeFlare -->|webhook<br/>cert rotation| CertController[cert-controller<br/>Latest<br/>REQUIRED]
    CodeFlare -->|CRD watch<br/>resource mgmt| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    CodeFlare -.->|workload<br/>scheduling<br/>quota mgmt| Kueue[Kueue<br/>v0.8.1<br/>OPTIONAL]
    CodeFlare -.->|external<br/>routes| OSRoute[OpenShift Route API<br/>v1<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|UI mgmt<br/>RayCluster creation| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Internal ODH]
    CodeFlare -->|user<br/>authentication| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>Internal ODH]
    CodeFlare -->|metrics<br/>scraping| Monitoring[OpenShift Monitoring<br/>Internal ODH]

    %% Integration Points (Bidirectional)
    KubeRay <-.->|reads<br/>RayCluster status| CodeFlare
    Kueue <-.->|Workload CRD<br/>admission status| CodeFlare

    %% Managed Resources (Created by CodeFlare)
    CodeFlare ==>|creates| RayCluster[RayCluster Resources<br/>• OAuth Proxy<br/>• mTLS Secrets<br/>• NetworkPolicies<br/>• Routes/Ingress]
    CodeFlare ==>|manages| AppWrapper[AppWrapper Resources<br/>• Kueue Workloads<br/>• Wrapped Jobs/Clusters]

    %% User entry points
    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates CRs| Dashboard
    User -->|kubectl apply| K8sAPI
    Dashboard -->|creates| CodeFlare
    K8sAPI -->|watch events| CodeFlare

    %% Component relationships
    KubeRay -->|creates| RayPods[Ray Head/Worker Pods]
    RayCluster -.->|includes| RayPods

    %% Styling
    style CodeFlare fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff
    style KubeRay fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style CertController fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Kueue fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5,color:#333
    style OSRoute fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5,color:#333
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style OAuth fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Monitoring fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style RayCluster fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style AppWrapper fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style User fill:#08427b,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style RayPods fill:#dae8fc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,color:#000

